videoSnippet.title: I Paired Stockfish NNUE Against Chessmaster "Grandmaster Edition"
videoSnippet.description:
Watch previous match here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=386uUj4lN8Q

Read up on NNUE Stockfish here https://www.chess.com/blog/the_real_greco/evolution-of-a-chess-fish-what-is-nnue-anyway#:~:text=What%20does%20NNUE%20stand%20for,NNUE%20is%20wordplay%20in%20Japanese.

Have a great day :)

Stockfish 14 + NNUE vs Chessmaster GM Edition
Friendly Game
C70 Ruy Lopez, Caro variation

1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 Nc6 3.Bb5 a6 4.Ba4 b5 5.Bb3 Nf6 6.d4 exd4 7.O-O d6 8.Ng5 Ne5 9.f4 Nc4 10.e5 dxe5 11.Bxc4 bxc4 12.fxe5 Bb7 13.exf6 gxf6 14.Re1+ Be7 15.Ne4 h5 16.Nxf6+ Kf8 17.Qd2 Bxf6 18.Qb4+ Kg7 19.Qxb7 d3 20.c3 Qd6 21.Qf3 Rae8 22.Rf1 Re6 23.Bf4 Qb6+ 24.Kh1 Qxb2 25.Nd2 Rhe8 26.Rab1 Qxa2 27.Qxh5 Kg8 28.Bh6 Bxc3 29.Qxf7+ Kh8 30.Rb4 R6e7 31.Qh5 Kg8 32.Qg4+ Bg7 33.Qg6 Rd8 34.Bg5 Ra8 35.Bxe7 Qxd2 36.Rfb1 Qxb4 37.Bxb4 Kh8 38.Rf1 d2 39.Bxd2 Rb8 40.Rf7 Rb1+ 41.Qxb1 c5 42.Qg6 a5 43.Qxg7
